metadata.title: Vitalik Buterin TC 2017
metadata.name: Vitalik Buterin TC 2017
metadata.description: This NFT is for the Vitalik Buterin 2017 TC bobblehead. This NFT comes with a PHYSICAL ITEM that will be shipped upon purchase. Items will be shipped only to the US, currently we do not offer international shipping. To receive the physical item, follow the redemption instructions below. Redemption Instructions: 1. Purchase Proof of Bobble NFT on OpenSea. 2. Go to Proofofbobble.com/pages/redeem and fill out the redemption form. 3. Proof of Bobble will give you the specific unique ETH wallet for the owner to send the NFT to for redemption. 4. The NFT will be transferred to a paper wallet, affixed to the item purchased by Proof of Bobble, then shipped to the owner of the collectible. Special Note: Proof of Bobble can only ship to U.S addresses at this time.
